jvmtiCapabilities Struct Reference

#include <jvmti_types.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

Bit table of JVMTI capabilities supported by VM.

See <a href="http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.5.0/docs/guide/jvmti/jvmti.html.jvmtiCapabilities>specification for details.
